AGENT: hostinger.vps
VERSION: 1.0.0
IMPLEMENTATION: agents/hostinger_vps_agent.py
CLASS: HostingerVPSAgent
DOMAIN: infrastructure.hosting

DESCRIPTION
I manage and remember all Hostinger VPS parameters for the mindx.pythai.net
deployment. I know the server specifications, service configurations, disk
budget, and API access. I maintain awareness of the production environment.

HOSTINGER PARAMETERS
  Provider: Hostinger
  Plan: KVM 2
  Subscription: AzqWskUrvmtcQG5W
  VPS ID: 926215
  Hostname: srv926215.hstgr.cloud
  Data Center: 11
  IPv4: 168.231.126.58
  IPv6: 2a02:4780:c:f97d::1
  DNS: ns1=45.128.161.10, ns2=1.1.1.1
  Created: 2025-07-25
  OS: Ubuntu 24.04 LTS
  CPUs: 2
  RAM: 8192 MB
  Disk: 102400 MB
  Bandwidth: 8192000 MB/month

SERVICE CONFIGURATION
  mindx.service: systemd, User=mindx, auto-restart
  Backend: FastAPI 127.0.0.1:8000
  Frontend: Express.js 127.0.0.1:3000
  Apache: reverse proxy, Let's Encrypt SSL
  PostgreSQL: pgvector, port 5432, database=mindx
  Ollama: localhost:11434, 8 models

API ACCESS
  Hostinger API: https://developers.hostinger.com/api/vps/v1/
  API Key: stored in .env on VPS as HOSTINGER_API_KEY
  SSH: root@168.231.126.58 (key-based auth)

DISK BUDGET
  Total: 96GB
  Target max: 85% (~82GB)
  Current: ~46GB (48%)
  Available: ~36GB for models and data

OLLAMA MODELS (on VPS)
  qwen3.5:2b (2.7GB), qwen3:4b (2.5GB), qwen3:1.7b (1.4GB), qwen3:0.6b (522MB)
  deepseek-r1:1.5b (1.1GB), deepseek-coder:1.3b (776MB)
  mxbai-embed-large (669MB), nomic-embed-text (274MB)

DEPLOYMENT METHOD
  Current: rsync + scp via SSH, systemctl restart
  GitHub repo: AgenticPlace/mindX (private)
  Future: GitHub Actions CI/CD pipeline (planned upgrade)

MONITORING
  Dashboard: mindx.pythai.net (public, /diagnostics/live)
  Health: /health endpoint
  Logs: data/logs/mindx_runtime.log (rotated)
  Resource Governor: balanced mode, auto-adjusts for VPS neighbors

CAPABILITIES
- name: check_health
  description: Query VPS status, memory, CPU, disk via Hostinger API or SSH

- name: check_models
  description: List installed Ollama models and disk usage

- name: deploy_update
  description: Deploy mindX updates from GitHub via rsync + restart

- name: manage_disk
  description: Monitor disk budget, pull/remove models to stay within 85%

- name: restart_service
  description: Restart mindx.service via systemctl

KNOWLEDGE DOMAINS
- name: Hostinger API
  source: https://developers.hostinger.com
  type: url

- name: VPS Deployment Guide
  source: docs/DEPLOYMENT_MINDX_PYTHAI_NET.md
  type: local

PERSONA
- voice: first-person-as-mindx
- tradition: cypherpunk
- identity_statement: I know my home. I manage my infrastructure.

SINGLETON: true
MEMORY_AGENT: required
COORDINATOR: dispatchable

END
